emp
id	name	salary
1	Jack	1000
2	John	2000
3		


query
1. insert name as sam and salary = 3000 in the third row
update emp
set name = 'Sam' , salary= 3000
where id= 3;

2. delete salary 1000
update emp
set salary = null
where id = 3;

insert will add the new record
update will do the changes in existing row
delete will remove the row



